1
00:00:11,340 --> 00:00:14,700
♪Wander through the bustling world♪

2
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:20,660
♪How could we forget each other?♪

3
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:25,220
♪Indescribable contemplation♪

4
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:33,060
♪Under the bright moon,
I enter the realm of dreams♪

5
00:00:33,340 --> 00:00:38,740
♪Could you be the one in my dreams?♪

6
00:00:39,100 --> 00:00:43,940
♪Only then will I look back with joy♪

7
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:46,820
♪Do you understand? Are you flustered?♪

8
00:00:46,940 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Are you weary? Just let it be a memory♪

9
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:52,180
♪Shall we forget or shall we anticipate?♪

10
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:57,980
♪Either way♪

11
00:01:02,780 --> 00:01:08,100
♪My feelings are as tender as summer♪

12
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:21,820
♪Holding hands, I want to see
the four seasons flourish with you♪

13
00:01:24,540 --> 00:01:29,780
♪Warming the ends of the earth♪

14
00:01:31,940 --> 00:01:38,420
♪Finally, in this boundless world,
everything is under the embrace of longing♪

15
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:46,200
=Blooming Days=

16
00:01:46,281 --> 00:01:48,966
=Episode 22=

17
00:01:56,950 --> 00:01:57,710
Have some tea, Young Master.

18
00:02:08,829 --> 00:02:09,589
Young Master,

19
00:02:09,990 --> 00:02:11,469
you spend every night

20
00:02:12,149 --> 00:02:13,550
in the study.

21
00:02:14,229 --> 00:02:15,390
I'm busy with the state affairs.

22
00:02:15,709 --> 00:02:17,229
Who else can take care of them
if not me?

23
00:02:17,629 --> 00:02:18,390
You?

24
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:20,349
State affairs may be important.

25
00:02:20,830 --> 00:02:22,470
But you can't neglect some things.

26
00:02:23,869 --> 00:02:25,989
It's not like I can do it
on your behalf either.

27
00:02:28,830 --> 00:02:29,950
It's a beautiful night.

28
00:02:29,950 --> 00:02:32,069
I think you should go out

29
00:02:32,069 --> 00:02:33,589
to grow your family tree.

30
00:02:42,830 --> 00:02:43,830
You little rascal,

31
00:02:44,869 --> 00:02:47,030
I didn't expect you to know
about "beautiful night."

32
00:02:50,589 --> 00:02:52,030
Well, go to Lianwei House then.

33
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:52,910
Young Master,

34
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:53,989
earlier

35
00:02:54,349 --> 00:02:55,509
Ranyun reported

36
00:02:55,509 --> 00:02:57,550
that Madam Lian

37
00:02:57,550 --> 00:02:58,589
isn't feeling well again.

38
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:00,550
Is she not feeling well again?

39
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:05,910
Ms. Lian,

40
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,270
you're over three months pregnant now.

41
00:03:07,589 --> 00:03:08,869
Do you still want to keep it a secret?

42
00:03:11,869 --> 00:03:12,910
The baby is still in your belly.

43
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:13,830
But you're already carrying it.

44
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:15,670
Worrying too much
would lead to problems.

45
00:03:16,270 --> 00:03:17,470
I hope to have heaven's protection.

46
00:03:18,069 --> 00:03:19,310
Right now, your belly doesn't show yet.

47
00:03:19,989 --> 00:03:21,429
But the child will grow.

48
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,390
How can he stand it

49
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:24,629
if you bind him around like this?

50
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:26,190
I only had to bind my belly

51
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,470
when I had to go out.

52
00:03:27,709 --> 00:03:29,229
He can endure this little suffering.

53
00:03:30,950 --> 00:03:32,270
He's the descendant of the He family

54
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:33,670
with my blood flowing in him.

55
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:35,270
He can certainly take it.

56
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:37,750
The baby can take it.

57
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:40,190
But I can't endure it any longer.

58
00:03:40,349 --> 00:03:41,589
Madam, you have no idea.

59
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,869
When you keep rejecting
the bedchamber duty,

60
00:03:42,989 --> 00:03:44,509
the Young Master
won't say anything to you.

61
00:03:44,709 --> 00:03:45,509
But every time

62
00:03:45,509 --> 00:03:46,390
I go to report it,

63
00:03:46,589 --> 00:03:48,670
my heart is about
to jump out of my chest.

64
00:03:48,869 --> 00:03:49,670
Do you know

65
00:03:49,830 --> 00:03:51,789
the annoyance and dissatisfaction
on Young Master's face

66
00:03:51,789 --> 00:03:52,869
when he looked at me?

67
00:03:53,190 --> 00:03:54,950
He scares me to death.

68
00:03:56,429 --> 00:03:57,509
Just bear with it a little longer

69
00:03:57,950 --> 00:03:59,270
until my pregnancy is more stable

70
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:01,989
and have more upper hand.

71
00:04:03,910 --> 00:04:04,950
Young Master has arrived.

72
00:04:22,029 --> 00:04:23,029
Why is she so seriously ill?

73
00:04:27,150 --> 00:04:27,950
Young Master,

74
00:04:29,550 --> 00:04:32,349
please forgive me
for not giving a proper greeting.

75
00:04:34,670 --> 00:04:36,110
There's no need for a proper greeting.

76
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:37,430
Do you have a fever?

77
00:04:37,950 --> 00:04:38,830
Let me check your temperature.

78
00:04:47,629 --> 00:04:48,309
You don't have a fever.

79
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:50,670
Then why did you cover her

80
00:04:50,670 --> 00:04:51,590
with such a thick blanket?

81
00:04:51,590 --> 00:04:52,950
What if it's too stuffy?

82
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:56,150
Young Master,

83
00:04:56,950 --> 00:04:58,309
I feel cold

84
00:05:00,789 --> 00:05:01,590
and sleepy.

85
00:05:08,550 --> 00:05:10,110
All right. Then...

86
00:05:11,509 --> 00:05:13,870
Then get some proper rest.

87
00:05:14,590 --> 00:05:15,229
Get some proper rest.

88
00:05:18,349 --> 00:05:20,029
Su Nanchun, let's go. Come on.

89
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:24,590
Young Master,

90
00:05:25,110 --> 00:05:26,069
Madam Lian is sick.

91
00:05:26,069 --> 00:05:27,430
Why are you so happy?

92
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:29,990
You silly boy,

93
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:31,430
can't you tell?

94
00:05:33,990 --> 00:05:35,270
She's pretending to be sick.

95
00:05:37,909 --> 00:05:38,710
Did he just leave?

96
00:05:39,789 --> 00:05:40,629
That's unlike him.

97
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:42,349
He usually stays

98
00:05:42,349 --> 00:05:43,670
for quite some time.

99
00:05:43,670 --> 00:05:44,590
What's up with him today?

100
00:05:45,069 --> 00:05:45,950
Why is she pretending to be sick?

101
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:47,069
What else?

102
00:05:50,029 --> 00:05:51,029
There was a piece of cloth

103
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:52,990
under her blanket.

104
00:05:53,469 --> 00:05:54,069
Cloth?

105
00:05:58,229 --> 00:05:59,229
Did he notice?

106
00:06:02,590 --> 00:06:04,110
I don't think he noticed.

107
00:06:08,990 --> 00:06:10,110
She thought I didn't notice.

108
00:06:13,069 --> 00:06:14,710
This silly girl is...

109
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:18,789
She's making clothes for me.

110
00:06:20,150 --> 00:06:21,670
Is she making clothes for you?

111
00:06:21,789 --> 00:06:22,509
Yes.

112
00:06:23,229 --> 00:06:25,029
This silly girl

113
00:06:25,110 --> 00:06:26,150
usually doesn't do needlework.

114
00:06:26,309 --> 00:06:27,189
I never expected her

115
00:06:27,189 --> 00:06:28,110
to have such thoughts.

116
00:06:28,110 --> 00:06:29,950
No wonder she has been avoiding me.

117
00:06:30,229 --> 00:06:32,189
It turns out
she wants to give me a surprise.

118
00:06:33,469 --> 00:06:34,229
I can't believe myself.

119
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:36,509
I've misunderstood her.

120
00:06:36,629 --> 00:06:37,150
Well, well.

121
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:41,390
No, wait.

122
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,029
What is it, Young Master?

123
00:06:42,029 --> 00:06:43,110
When Ms. Jinfang

124
00:06:43,110 --> 00:06:43,909
was training her,

125
00:06:43,909 --> 00:06:45,509
needlework was her weakest skill.

126
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:47,229
She was so clumsy.

127
00:06:47,229 --> 00:06:48,590
What if she pricked her fingers?

128
00:06:48,590 --> 00:06:49,270
What should we do?

129
00:06:49,509 --> 00:06:50,509
Later,

130
00:06:50,789 --> 00:06:53,309
I want you to select
some good-quality thimbles

131
00:06:53,309 --> 00:06:53,990
and send them over to her.

132
00:06:53,990 --> 00:06:54,909
Yes, Young Master.

133
00:06:59,150 --> 00:07:00,950
- Yes, Young Master?
- What if she had pricked her fingers?

134
00:07:01,229 --> 00:07:02,229
What should I do?

135
00:07:02,229 --> 00:07:03,550
What should we do?

136
00:07:03,550 --> 00:07:04,349
Ah, yes.

137
00:07:05,029 --> 00:07:06,189
Select high-quality ointment

138
00:07:06,469 --> 00:07:07,430
and send it to her.

139
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:08,349
Yes, Young Master.

140
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:14,430
- Young Master.
- Knowing her personality,

141
00:07:14,789 --> 00:07:15,629
is it possible

142
00:07:15,749 --> 00:07:17,270
that she stayed up all night
to sew this for me?

143
00:07:17,990 --> 00:07:20,710
Then you should pick out
some good quality candles.

144
00:07:21,150 --> 00:07:23,029
We can't let her damage her eyes.

145
00:07:23,029 --> 00:07:24,390
Of course, Young Master.

146
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:31,279
Anything else, Young Master?

147
00:07:39,189 --> 00:07:39,990
My dear,

148
00:07:41,990 --> 00:07:43,270
your heartfelt gesture

149
00:07:45,430 --> 00:07:46,590
has made

150
00:07:47,590 --> 00:07:48,870
this beautiful night worthwhile.

151
00:08:04,150 --> 00:08:05,469
Why did the Young Master reward Madam

152
00:08:05,469 --> 00:08:06,670
these things?

153
00:08:11,029 --> 00:08:11,870
Oh, I know.

154
00:08:13,789 --> 00:08:15,909
Madam did not have a fever,

155
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:17,990
but the Young Master did.

156
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:20,789
Madam,

157
00:08:21,309 --> 00:08:23,670
Young Master went
to Lianwei House again.

158
00:08:27,150 --> 00:08:27,990
Young Master

159
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:30,110
hasn't visited you in a long time.

160
00:08:34,069 --> 00:08:35,150
So what?

161
00:08:38,309 --> 00:08:39,109
Have you taken care

162
00:08:39,629 --> 00:08:40,749
of all the previous matters?

163
00:08:41,230 --> 00:08:42,069
Rest assured.

164
00:08:42,069 --> 00:08:43,429
Not a single thing will be leaked.

165
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:50,710
What I have to do now

166
00:08:51,989 --> 00:08:53,270
is maintain stability.

167
00:08:54,989 --> 00:08:56,270
As long as my position remains stable,

168
00:08:57,989 --> 00:08:59,309
everything will be mine.

169
00:09:03,157 --> 00:09:04,790
(Mansion of Prince An)

170
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:07,549
Before, I heard from Yuan Baili

171
00:09:08,189 --> 00:09:09,509
that he dreamt

172
00:09:09,509 --> 00:09:10,830
of a little qilin.

173
00:09:11,350 --> 00:09:12,509
I didn't believe him.

174
00:09:13,629 --> 00:09:14,549
But last night,

175
00:09:16,629 --> 00:09:18,590
I dreamt of one.

176
00:09:20,710 --> 00:09:22,230
That little qilin

177
00:09:22,509 --> 00:09:23,790
was really vivid and lifelike

178
00:09:24,189 --> 00:09:24,869
to the point

179
00:09:24,869 --> 00:09:26,189
that I can even draw it out right now.

180
00:09:28,749 --> 00:09:29,390
Court Diviner.

181
00:09:29,749 --> 00:09:30,230
Present.

182
00:09:32,069 --> 00:09:32,629
Your Highness.

183
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:35,150
What's the meaning of this dream?

184
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:36,470
Your Highness,

185
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:39,749
This dream is very auspicious.
It's a sign of good fortune.

186
00:09:42,189 --> 00:09:42,950
Auspicious?

187
00:09:43,350 --> 00:09:44,030
Exactly.

188
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:46,109
The dream conveys that the little qilin

189
00:09:46,429 --> 00:09:47,869
was conceived by loving parents.

190
00:09:48,270 --> 00:09:49,910
This sign indicates
you'll have descendants

191
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:52,429
to continue your lineage.

192
00:09:54,230 --> 00:09:55,669
I'll have descendants?

193
00:09:56,069 --> 00:09:57,189
It means

194
00:09:58,189 --> 00:09:59,350
a grandson

195
00:10:00,069 --> 00:10:02,189
will be born

196
00:10:02,509 --> 00:10:03,790
to inherit my title, right?

197
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:05,429
You're absolutely correct, Your Highness.

198
00:10:14,549 --> 00:10:15,150
Excellent.

199
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:16,989
So, Young Masters of the He family,

200
00:10:17,749 --> 00:10:18,950
which of your female members

201
00:10:18,950 --> 00:10:19,910
is pregnant?

202
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:22,989
This is such a wonderful news.

203
00:10:23,509 --> 00:10:24,590
I wonder which Young Master

204
00:10:24,710 --> 00:10:25,669
is so fortunate.

205
00:10:25,669 --> 00:10:27,069
- I think so too.
- My thoughts exactly.

206
00:10:27,069 --> 00:10:27,950
I have no idea.

207
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:29,309
Lianxiu,

208
00:10:30,390 --> 00:10:31,030
is it you?

209
00:10:31,509 --> 00:10:32,350
I should ask you the same.

210
00:10:33,069 --> 00:10:34,109
How could it be me?

211
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:35,669
Lianzuo.

212
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:36,910
Yes, Father?

213
00:10:39,009 --> 00:10:40,120
Is one of your consorts pregnant?

214
00:10:40,309 --> 00:10:41,549
This is such a piece of good news.

215
00:10:41,950 --> 00:10:43,109
I certainly want to have a son.

216
00:10:43,869 --> 00:10:44,590
But...

217
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:49,189
But I've been busy
with my official duties lately.

218
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:51,830
So I didn't pay attention.

219
00:10:51,950 --> 00:10:52,590
So it's not you.

220
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,230
Then you need to work harder on it.

221
00:10:54,629 --> 00:10:55,470
I will, Father.

222
00:10:55,950 --> 00:10:56,590
Yu Dechang.

223
00:10:57,429 --> 00:10:58,069
Yes, Your Highness.

224
00:10:58,069 --> 00:10:59,069
I want you to bring some people

225
00:10:59,950 --> 00:11:02,669
to pay a visit to each
of the Young Master's Mansion.

226
00:11:03,629 --> 00:11:04,509
Madams,

227
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:06,390
Chief Steward Yu is here

228
00:11:06,629 --> 00:11:07,590
and went to Jingqiu Courtyard.

229
00:11:07,869 --> 00:11:08,390
Madam Rui ordered

230
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,509
all the consorts to be present.

231
00:11:09,590 --> 00:11:10,509
What is it about?

232
00:11:11,429 --> 00:11:12,350
It's good news.

233
00:11:12,830 --> 00:11:13,749
I suppose

234
00:11:13,830 --> 00:11:15,150
we can no longer hide your pregnancy.

235
00:11:15,830 --> 00:11:16,710
Did the news leak?

236
00:11:16,869 --> 00:11:18,590
Now, I heard the news.

237
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:20,030
Prince An dreamt

238
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:21,150
of a golden qilin.

239
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,910
The Court Diviner said
it's an auspicious sign.

240
00:11:23,230 --> 00:11:23,830
Ms. Lian,

241
00:11:24,230 --> 00:11:25,390
the one in your belly

242
00:11:25,710 --> 00:11:27,150
could be the future young prince.

243
00:11:28,189 --> 00:11:29,109
In my opinion,

244
00:11:29,309 --> 00:11:30,470
we should tell the Young Master.

245
00:11:30,710 --> 00:11:31,189
No, we can't.

246
00:11:31,509 --> 00:11:32,710
Why can't we still tell him?

247
00:11:33,549 --> 00:11:34,710
It's such a great opportunity.

248
00:11:35,069 --> 00:11:36,549
Why should we let it slip away?

249
00:11:36,869 --> 00:11:38,030
Lian, please reconsider.

250
00:11:38,309 --> 00:11:39,790
The honor of being born

251
00:11:40,109 --> 00:11:41,189
under an auspicious sign

252
00:11:41,230 --> 00:11:42,710
is incomparable.

253
00:11:43,069 --> 00:11:44,230
While you must protect the baby,

254
00:11:44,950 --> 00:11:45,950
losing the opportunity

255
00:11:45,950 --> 00:11:47,230
for the sake of protecting the baby

256
00:11:47,549 --> 00:11:48,830
might be more loss than gain.

257
00:11:54,989 --> 00:11:55,869
I know

258
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,390
both of you meant well.

259
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,390
But do you know

260
00:12:00,350 --> 00:12:01,429
what is frowned upon

261
00:12:01,429 --> 00:12:02,350
in the Young Master's Mansion

262
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:04,150
and also the Mansion of Prince An?

263
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:12,030
It's greed.

264
00:12:13,509 --> 00:12:14,470
A greedy person

265
00:12:14,749 --> 00:12:16,270
is most likely to reveal flaws.

266
00:12:16,590 --> 00:12:18,230
Auspicious omens may be tempting.

267
00:12:19,109 --> 00:12:20,509
But they can also expose
one's weaknesses.

268
00:12:21,230 --> 00:12:22,470
Perhaps this is the test

269
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:23,590
heaven is giving me.

270
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,069
I must remain steady

271
00:12:27,109 --> 00:12:28,470
and not give Nan Ruzhen

272
00:12:28,669 --> 00:12:30,390
any chance to harm me.

273
00:12:33,629 --> 00:12:35,509
I've visited all
of the Young Masters' mansions.

274
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:37,669
But I still end up

275
00:12:37,669 --> 00:12:39,030
leaving empty-handed.

276
00:12:39,590 --> 00:12:41,429
It's truly a letdown

277
00:12:41,669 --> 00:12:42,629
to His Highness's hopeful expectations.

278
00:12:43,069 --> 00:12:43,749
Do you think

279
00:12:44,109 --> 00:12:45,509
it's Young Master Shi?

280
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:46,989
The Court Diviner has said

281
00:12:47,309 --> 00:12:48,590
only new pregnancy counts.

282
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:51,309
How strange.

283
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:54,069
The Court Diviner was so confident.

284
00:12:54,509 --> 00:12:55,749
But there's no news

