00:30:44,590 --> 00:30:45,549
(what he said to me?)

567
00:30:49,069 --> 00:30:49,830
(Mr. Lv,)

568
00:30:50,389 --> 00:30:51,429
(Lady Xue asked me)

569
00:30:51,429 --> 00:30:52,230
(to deliver this to you.)

570
00:30:56,553 --> 00:30:59,553
(Yuanxue)

571
00:31:05,750 --> 00:31:07,269
(This is the first time)

572
00:31:08,429 --> 00:31:09,669
I've ever seen the moon outside

573
00:31:09,669 --> 00:31:10,710
since I was born.

574
00:31:12,069 --> 00:31:13,069
The place where I live

575
00:31:15,389 --> 00:31:18,309
is a tomb

576
00:31:18,870 --> 00:31:20,069
filled with beautiful clothes
and jewelry.

577
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:23,189
(There is only one way to leave,)

578
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:25,990
(which is to marry)

579
00:31:26,309 --> 00:31:27,350
(a high-ranking official)

580
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:28,429
(I've never met before)

581
00:31:28,909 --> 00:31:30,269
(and go to another tomb.)

582
00:31:35,350 --> 00:31:35,950
(Yuanxue.)

583
00:31:37,510 --> 00:31:38,309
(Lv Beiyi.)

584
00:31:40,710 --> 00:31:42,669
(Is this your current state of mind?)

585
00:31:44,350 --> 00:31:45,630
(He said someone like you,)

586
00:31:45,750 --> 00:31:47,510
(who claims to love him.)

587
00:31:48,029 --> 00:31:49,590
Yet, she's marrying to become
another man's wife.

588
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:51,029
A woman like this,

589
00:31:51,189 --> 00:31:52,230
even if she still

590
00:31:52,230 --> 00:31:53,269
has the slightest affection for him

591
00:31:53,710 --> 00:31:55,510
he still finds her utterly repulsive.

592
00:31:56,909 --> 00:31:57,830
Repulsive?

593
00:31:59,389 --> 00:32:00,950
(He said I was repulsive?)

594
00:32:02,669 --> 00:32:03,429
Yuanxue,

595
00:32:05,189 --> 00:32:07,149
I know you're pure and virtuous,

596
00:32:07,630 --> 00:32:09,429
who cares not about material wealth.

597
00:32:13,389 --> 00:32:14,269
Perhaps

598
00:32:16,990 --> 00:32:18,750
this is your best dowry.

599
00:32:20,149 --> 00:32:21,309
(No, Lv Beiyi.)

600
00:32:22,470 --> 00:32:23,389
(Qingkang Hall)
(This is unlike you.)

601
00:32:24,069 --> 00:32:25,710
(Lianxiu's lies won't deceive me.)

602
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:28,909
(But what he said)

603
00:32:30,789 --> 00:32:32,350
(is the truth.)

604
00:32:43,269 --> 00:32:44,269
Forgive me for no longer being able

605
00:32:45,149 --> 00:32:47,110
to perform my duty as a child.

606
00:32:48,149 --> 00:32:51,149
I hope you will take care
of your health,

607
00:32:52,630 --> 00:32:53,870
and not worry about me.

608
00:32:57,870 --> 00:33:00,309
When a daughter grows up,
they have to marry eventually.

609
00:33:02,029 --> 00:33:04,110
The husband I've chosen for you

610
00:33:05,069 --> 00:33:06,750
is considered a talented man.

611
00:33:07,870 --> 00:33:08,669
I believe you

612
00:33:09,669 --> 00:33:10,750
would be satisfied with him.

613
00:33:35,189 --> 00:33:36,630
You've always been clever

614
00:33:37,470 --> 00:33:38,669
and have high ambitions.

615
00:33:41,549 --> 00:33:42,830
But after today,

616
00:33:44,269 --> 00:33:45,230
you'll be a daughter-in-law

617
00:33:45,230 --> 00:33:46,870
in someone else's house.

618
00:33:48,149 --> 00:33:50,069
You must fulfill your wifely duties
with the utmost diligence,

619
00:33:51,309 --> 00:33:52,870
without the slightest negligence.

620
00:33:54,950 --> 00:33:57,429
You don't have to worry
about matters here.

621
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:01,350
Your husband's mansion
is in Quliang.

622
00:34:02,510 --> 00:34:04,029
If you miss us,

623
00:34:05,590 --> 00:34:06,750
you can come home anytime.

624
00:34:13,070 --> 00:34:15,550
I shall remember your advice.

625
00:34:16,429 --> 00:34:17,429
I want

626
00:34:18,829 --> 00:34:19,950
to thank you

627
00:34:21,030 --> 00:34:22,589
for giving birth to me.

628
00:34:24,990 --> 00:34:26,109
Thank you

629
00:34:28,109 --> 00:34:29,869
for raising me all these years.

630
00:34:47,790 --> 00:34:48,510
Go.

631
00:34:50,389 --> 00:34:51,510
Don't miss the auspicious time.

632
00:35:53,790 --> 00:35:55,470
You went to Prince An's mansion
to retrieve the flask last night.

633
00:35:55,790 --> 00:35:56,550
Did you get it?

634
00:36:00,389 --> 00:36:01,149
Not yet.

635
00:36:02,429 --> 00:36:03,770
We need to take our time
to plan this out.

636
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:05,589
Why?

637
00:36:06,429 --> 00:36:07,310
Since when

638
00:36:07,310 --> 00:36:08,270
have you been this patient?

639
00:36:08,790 --> 00:36:09,990
If this matter leaks out,

640
00:36:10,470 --> 00:36:12,189
not only our overall situation
is at stake,

641
00:36:13,030 --> 00:36:14,270
but also your wealth and life.

642
00:36:17,550 --> 00:36:19,149
What did you do to Yuanxue?

643
00:36:24,470 --> 00:36:25,629
(As the daughter of Prince An,)

644
00:36:25,990 --> 00:36:26,909
(you're destined)

645
00:36:26,909 --> 00:36:28,349
(to never break away from the cage.)

646
00:36:29,189 --> 00:36:30,109
(To break free forever,)

647
00:36:30,109 --> 00:36:31,189
(there's only one option.)

648
00:36:36,550 --> 00:36:37,230
(Yuanxue,)

649
00:36:38,189 --> 00:36:38,909
(you can't!)

650
00:36:39,510 --> 00:36:40,230
Out of the way!

651
00:36:44,589 --> 00:36:46,550
Young Master, we're almost here.

652
00:36:47,270 --> 00:36:48,070
It looks like this task

653
00:36:48,070 --> 00:36:48,829
is going pretty smoothly.

654
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:50,909
It's surprisingly

655
00:36:51,189 --> 00:36:52,149
smooth.

656
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:53,429
Why did you say that?

657
00:36:53,550 --> 00:36:54,790
After all, this marriage

658
00:36:55,270 --> 00:36:56,950
isn't what Yuanxue wants.

659
00:36:57,189 --> 00:36:58,429
I hope I'm overthinking it.

660
00:37:19,990 --> 00:37:20,680
Move aside!

661
00:37:20,680 --> 00:37:21,950
- Move aside!
- Don't just stand there.

662
00:37:21,950 --> 00:37:23,030
Take that man down!

663
00:37:23,389 --> 00:37:24,470
If you want to save Lady Xue' life,

664
00:37:24,790 --> 00:37:25,750
move aside now!

665
00:37:26,230 --> 00:37:27,909
Lady Xue is poisoned
and in grave danger.

666
00:37:28,230 --> 00:37:29,389
We can't afford to delay any longer.

667
00:37:30,109 --> 00:37:30,909
Return to the Mansion of Prince!

668
00:37:32,790 --> 00:37:33,869
Is there no way at all?

669
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:35,990
Lady Xue consumed

670
00:37:36,109 --> 00:37:36,950
a highly toxic poison

671
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:38,149
in a large quantity.

672
00:37:38,669 --> 00:37:39,950
It's extremely difficult to treat.

673
00:37:41,270 --> 00:37:41,990
Indeed.

674
00:37:42,189 --> 00:37:43,990
Last night, when I was checking
the medicinal ingredients inventory

675
00:37:43,990 --> 00:37:45,149
at the Office of Medication,

676
00:37:45,669 --> 00:37:46,629
I noticed several components

677
00:37:46,829 --> 00:37:48,470
of the poison were missing.

678
00:37:48,869 --> 00:37:49,909
Who could have guessed

679
00:37:50,389 --> 00:37:51,829
it was the Lady Xue who took them?

680
00:37:52,310 --> 00:37:53,230
She consumed such a large amount.

681
00:37:53,909 --> 00:37:55,790
She's truly beyond saving now.

682
00:37:56,429 --> 00:37:57,510
Office of Medication?

683
00:38:03,589 --> 00:38:04,470
Our top priority

684
00:38:04,629 --> 00:38:05,790
is Yuanxue's life.

685
00:38:06,149 --> 00:38:06,790
Lv Beiyi,

686
00:38:07,349 --> 00:38:08,470
you're a skilled physician.

687
00:38:08,869 --> 00:38:09,550
Do you have a solution?

688
00:38:13,510 --> 00:38:14,669
Do you?

689
00:38:15,950 --> 00:38:16,950
We can only give it a try.

690
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:17,950
How are we going to try?

691
00:38:18,510 --> 00:38:19,429
Using poison to fight poison.

692
00:38:19,829 --> 00:38:20,950
Absolutely not!

693
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:22,510
That's right, Young Master.
You must think about this.

694
00:38:22,790 --> 00:38:23,510
Lv Beiyi,

695
00:38:24,389 --> 00:38:25,629
I was wrong to trust you before.

696
00:38:26,589 --> 00:38:27,070
Can

697
00:38:28,109 --> 00:38:29,189
I trust you again now?

698
00:38:29,389 --> 00:38:30,710
I was able to enter Prince An's mansion

699
00:38:31,669 --> 00:38:33,550
and stand here.

700
00:38:34,470 --> 00:38:35,270
Didn't I manage to do these

701
00:38:35,270 --> 00:38:36,389
because you trusted me?

702
00:38:36,869 --> 00:38:37,990
You trusted me from the beginning

703
00:38:38,310 --> 00:38:39,589
when I carried Lady Xue out

704
00:38:39,629 --> 00:38:40,990
from the wedding sedan.

705
00:38:44,270 --> 00:38:45,310
Do as he says.

706
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:48,829
I'll bear all the consequences.

707
00:39:03,109 --> 00:39:04,109
Father, forgive me.

708
00:39:04,270 --> 00:39:05,270
I failed in my duties.

709
00:39:08,990 --> 00:39:09,589
Father,

710
00:39:10,270 --> 00:39:10,909
Yuanxue is...

711
00:39:10,950 --> 00:39:11,750
Don't mention her.

712
00:39:14,710 --> 00:39:15,270
Your Highness,

713
00:39:15,869 --> 00:39:17,230
Madam Jing seeks an audience.

714
00:39:17,230 --> 00:39:17,829
Denied.

715
00:39:22,349 --> 00:39:24,389
She failed to educate her daughter.

716
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:25,710
How dare she come to see me?

717
00:39:26,429 --> 00:39:27,149
Your Highness,

718
00:39:28,389 --> 00:39:29,909
Lady Xue's life
is hanging by the thread.

719
00:39:30,470 --> 00:39:31,310
Madam Jing only wants you

720
00:39:31,310 --> 00:39:32,629
to see Lady Xue.

721
00:39:33,750 --> 00:39:35,589
Forgive me for being disrespectful.

722
00:39:36,470 --> 00:39:38,550
What if anything bad happens
to Lady Xue,

723
00:39:40,270 --> 00:39:42,589
it might be your last chance to see her.

724
00:39:47,230 --> 00:39:48,829
She doesn't respect me

725
00:39:48,829 --> 00:39:49,869
as her father,

726
00:39:50,589 --> 00:39:52,950
why should I go and see her?

727
00:39:54,470 --> 00:39:55,669
Before the wedding procession

728
00:39:56,070 --> 00:39:57,510
even entered the groom's residence,

729
00:39:58,750 --> 00:40:00,470
she had already taken her life
in the wedding sedan.

730
00:40:01,589 --> 00:40:02,589
By doing this,

731
00:40:03,750 --> 00:40:05,070
she deliberately aimed

732
00:40:05,070 --> 00:40:06,149
to tarnish my reputation in Quliang.

733
00:40:08,470 --> 00:40:09,710
From that moment on,

734
00:40:12,470 --> 00:40:13,869
she is no longer my daughter.

735
00:40:16,149 --> 00:40:17,109
Your Highness,

736
00:40:18,470 --> 00:40:21,109
please go and see Yuanxue.

737
00:40:22,270 --> 00:40:24,310
She is still unconscious.

738
00:40:24,950 --> 00:40:27,149
We don't know if she'll ever regain
her consciousness.

739
00:40:28,189 --> 00:40:30,550
We also don't know how long
we can keep her alive.

740
00:40:30,990 --> 00:40:34,990
Your Highness,
she may have made many mistakes.

741
00:40:35,470 --> 00:40:37,909
But she's still your flesh and blood.

742
00:40:38,990 --> 00:40:42,310
Are you really that heartless,
Your Highness?

743
00:40:42,990 --> 00:40:43,990
Please.

744
00:40:44,710 --> 00:40:46,030
I beg you.

745
00:40:48,349 --> 00:40:50,230
Please, Your Highness.

746
00:40:50,230 --> 00:40:50,790
Father,

747
00:40:52,109 --> 00:40:52,510
can't you...

748
00:40:52,510 --> 00:40:53,510
It's not your place to speak!

749
00:40:54,790 --> 00:40:55,950
I'm begging you.

750
00:40:56,710 --> 00:40:58,189
Is this how you complete your task?

751
00:41:01,510 --> 00:41:04,270
If I lose the trust of Quliang

752
00:41:04,869 --> 00:41:06,149
and my officials,

753
00:41:06,629 --> 00:41:07,470
then

754
00:41:08,710 --> 00:41:10,270
don't call me "Father" anymore.

755
00:41:15,030 --> 00:41:16,189
I shall take my leave.

756
00:41:43,941 --> 00:41:47,581
♪From the chaotic dust♪

757
00:41:47,581 --> 00:41:49,801
♪Gracefully stepping out♪

758
00:41:50,961 --> 00:41:54,031
♪Only then did I understand
the beauty of the world♪

759
00:41:54,671 --> 00:41:57,061
♪Why, and for what♪

760
00:41:58,011 --> 00:42:01,261
♪Holding pure intentions
in my heart♪

761
00:42:01,631 --> 00:42:04,441
♪Clinging to black and white♪

762
00:42:05,091 --> 00:42:07,921
♪Only then did I realize
that the path is simple♪

763
00:42:08,481 --> 00:42:11,001
♪It is love♪

764
00:42:11,871 --> 00:42:13,471
♪When fate♪

765
00:42:13,881 --> 00:42:16,711
♪Surges like deep clouds♪

766
00:42:18,951 --> 00:42:20,721
♪Regardless of♪

767
00:42:21,161 --> 00:42:22,641
♪What experiences may come♪

768
00:42:22,881 --> 00:42:27,561
♪Unable to linger♪

769
00:42:28,071 --> 00:42:30,041
♪Mountains and waves
are insignificant♪

770
00:42:30,041 --> 00:42:32,631
♪My promises to you remain♪

771
00:42:34,801 --> 00:42:38,481
♪Unafraid of obstacles
along this worldly path♪

772
00:42:38,781 --> 00:42:41,031
♪Worries are few♪

773
00:42:42,321 --> 00:42:44,151
♪The moon sets, stars scatter,
and mournful sounds ring♪

774
00:42:44,151 --> 00:42:47,891
♪My promises to you remain♪

775
00:42:48,781 --> 00:42:51,821
♪Life after life♪

776
00:42:52,921 --> 00:42:55,521
♪Will follow my heart's desires♪

777
00:42:57,321 --> 00:42:59,131
♪Forever unchanged♪
